                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-1383" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HAWKINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a biscuit-baker, and live in Tooley-street—the prisoner was my journeyman—I sent him to a wharf to get a sack of flour—I gave him two sovereigns, a half-crown, and 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he went out, and did not return, nor did the flour come.</p>
